        2/22/2010
    

Thats kind of funny what the last reviewer posted, as I travel between Toys r us to look for exclusive items. ( TF:A Arcee, old sets of exclusive star wars figures, etc ). I go as far as redwood city to find my little beauties, but who am I for you to listen to? Did i mention I live in milpitas, which is like 40 minutes away?This place has cheaper items, if you know what you're looking for. ( heres an actual comparison of two items that i found, star wars: Transformers at regular TRU, 12.99, at the express, 9.99. General grevious ) At the time i was buying them, regular Toys r Us stores had gotten rid of its old General transformers, and I was only able to find it at express. Oh, and by the way, sir, if you haven't noticed, LOTS OF WEBSITES THAT SELL THINGS ONLINE WILL BE CHEAPER. WHY? BECAUSE YOU PAY SHIPPING AND HANDLING.Holy crap, that dude had a vendetta against TRU, and this just irked me that the only review was from a nimrod.




