Contact Us 
 



For Customer Service Inquiries:
1 (800) TOYSRUS1 (800) 869-7787Corp.GuestServices@toysrus.com
Media Relations:
1 (973) 617-5900Press@toysrus.com
International Customers: Click on the Store Locator for contact information in your country. Mailing List: Would you like to be added or deleted from our mailing list? Changing your information on our mailing list is easy. Simply call 1-800-869-7787 and press option 6. Our automated system will walk you through the process.
If you’re a customer and looking for information about our policies, please visit the Help Desk. If you’re a customer and looking for the official rules of our Toys”R”Us Win $500 Survey Sweepstakes, please click here. 
