Home/Corporate Responsibility 





 corporate responsibility 






At Toys“R”Us, Inc., we are relentlessly striving to be the best toy and baby retail company for the world. 






In order to fulfill this mission, we demand integrity – from our team members, our executives, our business partners and our suppliers – in how we conduct ourselves and our business, every day.With global business operations comes global responsibility. Our citizenship initiatives are centered on issues where we can apply our resources as a worldwide retailer to make a profound impact in the communities we serve, all while continuing to deliver joy to children of all ages.Our key areas of focus include:

Diversity and Inclusion
Responsible Sourcing
Product Safety Standards and Practices
Charitable Giving
Disaster Aid and Response
 







