                            Toys "R" Us Outlet
                        

The Toys "R" Us Outlet at the Great Mall is the first of its kind in California. Selling the same top-quality toys and games as the main locations but with rotating discounts, the store offers an opportunity to stock up on kids' entertainment items.                    




STORE HOURS
Monday to Saturday 10AM–9PM  |  Sunday 11AM–8PM  |   




BEST ENTRANCE
Entrance 4
LOCATION IN MALL
462 - Located in Neighborhood 4 near the Dining Pavilion and Uniqlo



