My father orders my 2yr old a gift online, gives me the order #, then I drive 10 miles to pick up the item, then I am refused because it has to be the effen cardholder to pick it up! To top it all off the manager is a dick! doesn't even try to accomodate or try to speak with my father! Well maybe he shouldn't have because he would've gotten an earful of curse words his young arse never heard of.  ALTHOUGH, I cussed him out & threw a middle finger up in the air! SCREW YOU JOSH for being rude!

