I came here on a Tuesday afternoon to shop for a gift for my nephew and my niece.  A strong aircon breeze greeted me at the entrance.  It was awfully cold inside the store.  I walked in and strolled one aisle at a time, looking for new or extraordinary cute figurine toys.  To my surprise, they had limited selections and not as adorable as the ones I've seen at other stores.  In addition, their prices are expensive for an outlet store.Back to Target!




