This place has cheaper items, if you know what you're looking for. ( heres an actual comparison of two items that i found, star wars: Transformers at regular TRU, 12.99, at the express, 9.99. General grevious ) At the time i was buying them, regular Toys r Us stores had gotten rid of its old General transformers, and I was only able to find it at express. 

Oh, and by the way, sir, if you haven't noticed, LOTS OF WEBSITES THAT SELL THINGS ONLINE WILL BE CHEAPER. WHY? BECAUSE YOU PAY SHIPPING AND HANDLING.

Holy crap, that dude had a vendetta against TRU, and this just irked me that the only review was from a nimrod.







