        2/20/2014
    

I had to purchase tons of toys for our Kids Area. We needed big, durable toys. Jenna the Manager assisted us with finding what we were looking for. Being that we were going to carry tons of toys, she offered to let us borrow her flat bed cart. What a great idea! Jenna was really helpful, made it so much easier for us! Thank you Jenna for the great customer service. Once these toys get destroyed (in a few months) we will be back!




