        7/21/2011
    

The store & the store manager, Josh,in Hayward can kiss my arse! I've always hated coming to this store because of their poor customer service & their lack of popular items! Now I ULTIMATELY HATE TOYS R US! THEIR STUPID "order online & pick up at the store" sucks big balls! I'm sorry for the vulgarity but seriously Toys R Us has to rethink their "instore pickup" policy! My father orders my 2yr old a gift online, gives me the order #, then I drive 10 miles to pick up the item, then I am refused because it has to be the effen cardholder to pick it up! To top it all off the manager is a dick! doesn't even try to accomodate or try to speak with my father! Well maybe he shouldn't have because he would've gotten an earful of curse words his young arse never heard of.  ALTHOUGH, I cussed him out & threw a middle finger up in the air! SCREW YOU JOSH for being rude!I called the 800# & cancelled the order! Never again will I deal with Toys R Us! They're over priced & rude! THIS HONESTLY DOES NOT DESERVE A STAR!!!!




