        4/25/2011
    

This is not a real TRU.  This is like a TRU Express or something, can't remember what the associates called it.  Inventory here is hit and miss.  Its kinda like shopping for toys at Costco.  You don't know what they will have, and you can't depend on them to stock enough of any particular line of toy.  They have what they have.  This is primarily why I'm only giving them 2 stars.  However I have found rare figures here that I had trouble finding elsewhere.  So it is worth a visit every now and then.




